# TermiHUI Server Service Management

Service label: `studio.eugenezakharov.termihui-server`

## Stop the service

```bash
launchctl bootout gui/$(id -u)/studio.eugenezakharov.termihui-server
```

## Start the service

```bash
launchctl bootstrap gui/$(id -u) ~/Library/LaunchAgents/studio.eugenezakharov.termihui-server.plist
```

## Check if running

```bash
launchctl list | grep termihui-server
```

## Reinstall service

```bash
cd /Users/yevgeniyzakharov/Desktop/sources/termihui2/server && ./install.sh
```
